						<summary>

						<p>On a boulder near the <hi rend="italic">vāgu.</hi></p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1555 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1477, Rākshasa, Śrāvaṇa śu. 11, Thursday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1555 A.D., July 30</hi> which was <hi rend="bold">Tuesday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It seems to refer to the fixation of certain levies to be paid by the residents of the village Yallamanda in Koṇḍavīḍu-sīma by Siddhirāju Timmarājayya on behalf of Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Yaṟa Tirumalarājayya.</p>						

						</summary>
